{"tid":1670793,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"加泰事件總結","createTime":"2019-10-23T06:22:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T15:50:48.000Z","uid":201427,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"684506e8ad94fb210c378e94a30c19543b73980d","tid":1670793,"uid":201427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:22:38.000Z","msg":"如果集會主題係支持加泰獨立<br />\n香港會俾人聯想成想獨立/支持獨立<br />\n<br />\n如果係聲援加泰人反抗警暴/支持不同政見<br />\n香港會俾人覺得係追求民主自由<br />\n<br />\n講到依到自己諗去唔去啦<br />\n<br />\n同埋想講到少少關於香港獨立<br />\n美國其實唔係唔支持香港獨立<br />\n係香港未係時係獨立<br />\n因為佢地都要睇到香港可以發展到成熟既民主制度同人民有一定既政治思考能力<br />\n先夠膽俾香港獨立<br />\n同埋獨立既先決條件係要令現有中美利益平衡<br />\n所以香港獨立都係要有持續利益俾到中美先有可能獨立<br />\n<br />\n利申：個人對大家去唔去無意見<br />\n都係個句，兄弟爬山"},{"pid":"34640856d769c5ca5a94c241ad87ef8b87ff2fa3","tid":1670793,"uid":268462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:23:03.000Z","msg":"[可唔可以大和解］加泰搞手 全香港人求下你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1669934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1669934</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8a6579a3c34071de7e688974c76192a426af3f4a","tid":1670793,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34640856d769c5ca5a94c241ad87ef8b87ff2fa3","tid":1670793,"uid":268462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:23:03.000Z","msg":"[可唔可以大和解］加泰搞手 全香港人求下你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1669934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1669934</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:23:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26f621ce04ebd3b5b98e0d03505e06131591780b","tid":1670793,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:23:26.000Z","msg":"借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[晨早流流]三分鐘Twitter 戰線傳送門 10月23號<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1669882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1669882</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"76beea4a7fca5562b6be854c40abc9d6e2658d93","tid":1670793,"uid":201427,"l